OL,3,CMan jailed for shining laser at police
OL,4,Chelicopter
OL,6,FA man has been jailed after shining a
OL,7,Flaser beam at a police helicopter
OL,8,Fwhich was searching for a missing
OL,9,Fperson.
OL,11,FDavid Warren, 41, was sentenced to 35
OL,12,Fweeks when he appeared at Warrington
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court.
OL,15,FThe sentence includes 12 weeks for
OL,16,Fshining a laser beam towards an
OL,17,Faircraft, as well as activating a 23-
OL,18,Fweek suspended sentence for
OL,19,Fthreatening a person with a weapon.
