OL,3,CMan jailed for shining laser at police
OL,4,Chelicopter
OL,6,FIt was originally handed to him in
OL,7,FAugust, a week before he committed the
OL,8,Fsecond offence.
OL,10,FThe court heard that at around 1.30 on
OL,11,FTuesday 27 August, the police
OL,12,Fhelicopter was called in to search the
OL,13,Farea around Latchford and Stockton
OL,14,FHeath to help find a local man who was
OL,15,Fmissing.
OL,17,FJust before 3.15am, one of the
OL,18,Fofficers on board the helicopter
OL,19,Freported that a green laser light was
OL,20,Fbeing shone at the aircraft from the
OL,21,Fwindow of a property below.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
