OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F396A1727907543
OL,3,CMan jailed for shining laser at police
OL,4,Chelicopter
OL,6,FThe crew told ground controllers that
OL,7,Funless the suspect was stopped
OL,8,Fimmediately they would have to abandon
OL,9,Fthe search.
OL,11,FPolice on the ground traced the source
OL,12,Fof the light to the building where
OL,13,FWarren was but he refused to let them
OL,14,Fin.
OL,16,FHe was arrested after officers forced
OL,17,Ftheir way inside, also discovering a
OL,18,Fgreen laser.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
