OL,3,CMan jailed for shining laser at police
OL,4,Chelicopter
OL,6,FWarren, of Eagle Mount in Latchford,
OL,7,FWarrington, later admitted the offence
OL,8,Fto police, saying he was using the
OL,9,Flaser to point out the helicopter in
OL,10,Fthe sky while recording it on his
OL,11,Fphone.
OL,13,FHe was subsequently charged with
OL,14,Fshining a laser beam towards an
OL,15,Faircraft and pleaded guilty.
