OL,3,CMan jailed for shining laser at police
OL,4,Chelicopter
OL,6,FSergeant Michael Hayes said: "While
OL,7,Fthe person the police helicopter was
OL,8,Fsearching for during this incident was
OL,9,Fultimately located, shining the laser
OL,10,Fbeam in its direction was incredibly
OL,11,Fdangerous, and could have seriously
OL,12,Fhindered their efforts to locate
OL,13,Fsomeone in need of help.
OL,15,F"The sentence handed to Warren should
OL,16,Fserve as a reminder of how serious
OL,17,Fthis offence is considered.
